[38;5;129m│[0m scanning and exploitation. Traditional pentesting can be time-consuming and  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m resource-intensive, often requiring skilled professionals to manually probe  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m systems for weaknesses. An AI-based pentester can autonomously scan          [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m networks, applications, and devices, identifying potential vulnerabilities   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m with a high degree of accuracy. Once identified, the system can prioritize   [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m these vulnerabilities based on their severity and exploitability, providing  [38;5;129m│[0m
