[35m│[0m programs. The integration of AI in pentesting enhances efficiency, accuracy, [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m and the scope of security assessments.\n\n        AI-driven autonomous       [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m pentesters are designed to tackle CTF challenges, which are simulated        [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m environments created to test cybersecurity skills. These challenges often    [35m│[0m
